                    <h1>People</h1>
                    <p>The people who have served the Department of State represent a long and
                        complex tradition of U.S. diplomacy. This section contains a variety of
                        information about these people and their work. It includes the following: <ul>
                            <li>
                                <a href="$app/departmenthistory/people/secretaries">Biographies</a>
                                of the Secretaries of State and suggestions for further reading
                                about these public servants;</li>
                            <li>Extensive lists of the past <a
                                    href="$app/departmenthistory/people/principals-chiefs">Principal
                                    Officers of the Department of State and Chiefs of Mission</a>
                                organized by position, country, and name; </li>
                            <li>Details about the <a href="$app/departmenthistory/travels/secretary"
                                    >foreign travels of the Secretaries of State</a> and the <a
                                    href="$app/departmenthistory/travels/president">Presidents of
                                    the United States</a>; and,</li>
                            <li>Lists of the <a href="$app/departmenthistory/visits">visits of
                                    foreign leaders</a> to the United States.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
